01:52:43.469 --> 01:52:49.223
<i># I asked my sweetheart, What lies ahead?</i>

01:52:49.392 --> 01:52:54.219
<i># Will we have rainbows day after day</i>

01:52:54.397 --> 01:52:57.600
<i># Here's what my sweetheart said</i>

01:52:57.775 --> 01:53:01.725
<i># Que sera, sera</i>

01:53:01.904 --> 01:53:06.981
<i># Whatever will be, will be</i>

01:53:07.159 --> 01:53:11.406
<i># The future's not ours to see...</i>

01:53:11.581 --> 01:53:13.454
That's my mother's voice!

01:53:13.624 --> 01:53:16.958
<i>- That's my mother singing!
- What?</i>

01:53:18.963 --> 01:53:21.039
Are you sure, Hank?

01:53:21.215 --> 01:53:23.089
Are you quite sure?

01:53:23.259 --> 01:53:25.050
That's her! I know it!

01:53:27.638 --> 01:53:29.714
What's she doing here?

01:53:43.988 --> 01:53:46.859
Hank, can you whistle that song?

01:53:47.033 --> 01:53:49.025
I guess so.

01:53:51.579 --> 01:53:53.370
Then go on. Whistle it.

01:53:53.539 --> 01:53:56.991
Whistle it as loud as you can.

01:54:06.969 --> 01:54:08.761
<i># Will we have rainbows</i>

01:54:08.930 --> 01:54:12.133
<i># Day after day?</i>

01:54:12.308 --> 01:54:16.555
<i># Here's what my sweetheart said</i>

01:54:20.608 --> 01:54:24.606
<i># Ever will be, will be</i>

01:54:24.779 --> 01:54:28.278
<i># The future's not ours to see</i>

01:54:28.449 --> 01:54:30.691
<i># Que sera, sera</i>

01:54:31.869 --> 01:54:35.701
<i># What will be, will be</i>

01:54:35.873 --> 01:54:39.076
<i># Now I have children of my own</i>

01:54:39.252 --> 01:54:44.293
<i># They ask their mother, What will I be?</i>

