01:55:16.706 --> 01:55:20.205
You two wait in the mail
room. I'll bring him down.

01:55:22.378 --> 01:55:24.834
Give me about five minutes.

01:56:22.605 --> 01:56:23.850
No!

01:56:26.901 --> 01:56:28.940
Oh, Daddy!

01:56:31.197 --> 01:56:33.604
Take the boy. Go! But you must be quick!

01:56:33.783 --> 01:56:35.277
Come on, son.

01:56:39.747 --> 01:56:41.158
Don't touch him.

01:56:46.379 --> 01:56:48.455
I don't think you're
going to do any shooting,

01:56:48.631 --> 01:56:51.122
<i>not with these people
downstairs and police outside.</i>

01:56:51.300 --> 01:56:54.669
You're not in a very happy
position yourself, you know.

01:56:56.264 --> 01:57:00.392
- You've got to let the boy go!
- Precisely what I'm thinking.

01:57:00.560 --> 01:57:05.138
Now I'm sure you're going to be
sensible and help me out of here.

01:57:05.314 --> 01:57:07.805
Don't ask me for help, you miserable s-

01:57:07.984 --> 01:57:13.191
You wouldn't want your father
to get hurt, would you, Hank?

01:57:13.364 --> 01:57:17.314
<i>Now we're going to walk
downstairs together, casually,</i>

01:57:17.493 --> 01:57:19.818
like three old friends.

01:57:19.996 --> 01:57:24.040
Then we're going to take a stroll
as far as the nearest taxi rank.

01:57:24.208 --> 01:57:27.577
I hope there won't be any
emotional scenes on the way down.

01:57:27.753 --> 01:57:29.829
Do as he says, Hank.

01:57:31.841 --> 01:57:34.213
No, the other way. The other way.

01:57:34.385 --> 01:57:36.461
Shall we be going?

01:57:36.637 --> 01:57:38.963
All right, start down the hall, son.

01:57:41.726 --> 01:57:44.181
Don't say anything.

01:58:18.429 --> 01:58:23.056
<i># Now it's goodbye</i>

